OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome clear
OL,6,Fspells at first this evening, but soon
OL,7,Fturning cloudier with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain spreading northwards across most
OL,9,Fparts. Cloudy overnight with outbreaks
OL,10,Fof rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,13,Fsome patchy rain. Mainly dry in the
OL,14,Fafternoon with a few brighter spells
OL,15,Fin the south, but still a little rain
OL,16,Facross Argyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
