OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with showers and at times
OL,7,Flonger spells of heavier, more
OL,8,Fpersistent rain, though still with
OL,9,Fsome dry and bright spells. Winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening Tuesday, staying strong
OL,11,FWednesday and Thursday.
